         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the divine shades. To Gaius Porcius Dionysius; he lived 8 years, 10 months, and 13 days. Gaius Porcius Dionysius made this for his sweetest son.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
             <p>Line 2: missing interpunct after Porcio; contrast with interpunct in line 5 following
                 Porcius.</p>
             <p>Line 3: significant crack down the center of M.</p>
             <p>All letters in first
                 four lines have orange staining around the carving; line 5 retains this staining
                 until the "n"; line 6 until the "l" in dulcissimo; line 7 has no staining.</p>
         </div>
